This is my Java Library, but with added Classes for Android-use. Documentation can be found in "doc". Sources are found in "src".

To add this Library to your Android project (in Eclipse) follow these steps:
	1. Right-click the project.
	2. Click "Properties"
	3. On the side click "Android"
	4. Scroll down until you see the "Library" section
	5. Click "Add" and add this project.
	6. Close all the Windows you opened. :)